    <summary>
      <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-101">Rappresenta un convertitore che esegue l'associazione a dati per gestire la visibilità di pulsanti di ripetizione nei menu di scorrimento.</span>
      <span class="sxs-lookup">
        <span data-stu-id="43ad2-101">Represents a data-binding converter to handle the visibility of repeat buttons in scrolling menus.</span>
      </span>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-102">Il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> determina se un menu deve visualizzare i pulsanti di ripetizione quando un menu contiene troppi elementi per rientri nello schermo in una sola volta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> determines whether a menu should display the repeat buttons when a menu has too many items to fit on the screen at once.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-103">Usare il convertitore con un <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding> che ha quattro associazioni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-103">Use the converter with a <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding> that has four bindings.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-104">Le quattro associazioni devono essere alle proprietà dell'elemento padre <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer>: se le voci di menu sono organizzate in verticale (ovvero il valore predefinito per i menu), associare <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedVerticalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.VerticalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentHeight%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportHeight%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-104">The four bindings should be to properties of the parent <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer>:  If the menu items are organized vertically (which is the default for menus), bind to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedVerticalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.VerticalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentHeight%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportHeight%2A>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-105">Se le voci di menu vengono organizzate orizzontalmente, associare <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedHorizontalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.HorizontalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentWidth%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportWidth%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-105">If the menu items are organized horizontally, bind to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ComputedHorizontalScrollBarVisibility%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.HorizontalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ExtentWidth%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer.ViewportWidth%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-106">Impostare <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding.ConverterParameter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> su 0 o 100.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-106">Set <xref:System.Windows.Data.MultiBinding.ConverterParameter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to 0 or 100.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-107">Il valore viene considerato come una percentuale e determina se un pulsante viene nascosto quando il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> si trova nella posizione specificata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-107">The value is treated as a percentage and determines whether a button is hidden when the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the given location.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-108">Quando il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> si trovi all'inizio, la posizione del <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> è 0% e il pulsante in alto è nascosto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-108">When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the top, the position of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is 0% and the top button is hidden.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-109">Quando il <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> nella parte inferiore, la posizione del <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> equivale al 100% e il pulsante nella parte inferiore è nascosto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-109">When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is at the bottom, the position of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> is 100% and the bottom button is hidden.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-110">Nell'esempio seguente viene utilizzata la <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> nella <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> di un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> per un menu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-110">The following example uses the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MenuScrollingVisibilityConverter> in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> of a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ScrollViewer> for a menu.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="43ad2-111">Per un esempio completo, vedere [stile con ControlTemplates](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=160041).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43ad2-111">For the complete example, see [Styling with ControlTemplates Sample](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=160041).</span></span>  
  
